### ============================================
### 考试模块接口测试
### ⚠️ 请先注册一个学生账号并登录获取 student_token
### ============================================

# 学生账号：student1 / 123456（先注册一次）
# 教师账号：teacher1 / 123456

### ============================================
### 前置准备
### ============================================

### 0-1. 学生登录（获取 token）
POST http://localhost:8080/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student1",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 0-2. 学生注册（如果还没注册）
POST http://localhost:8080/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student1",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "student",
  "realName": "张三",
  "email": "student1@test.com"
}

### ============================================
### 考试流程测试
### ============================================

### 1. 开始考试（把 paperId 换成实际已发布试卷的 ID）
POST http://localhost:8080/exam/start
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2IiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJzdHVkZW50MSIsInJvbGUiOiJzdHVkZW50IiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzMzI0MDg2LCJleHAiOjE3ODM0MTA0ODZ9.i_Ok0y_P50oElRTVLM3JcIT1ngJYPUAeuLTZaA1suEY

{
  "paperId": 2074035342996443137
}

# 返回结果包含：
#   examRecordId — 考试记录ID，后续操作都要用
#   questions[] — 题目列表（不含正确答案）
#   duration — 考试时长（分钟）
#   resume — true=断点续考 false=新考试

###

### 2. 保存单题答案（可多次调用，每题单独保存）
POST http://localhost:8080/exam/answer
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2IiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJzdHVkZW50MSIsInJvbGUiOiJzdHVkZW50IiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzMzI0MDg2LCJleHAiOjE3ODM0MTA0ODZ9.i_Ok0y_P50oElRTVLM3JcIT1ngJYPUAeuLTZaA1suEY

{
  "examRecordId": 2074042573100019713,
  "questionId": 2074028794681323521,
  "userAnswer": "A"
}

###

### 2-2. 再保存第二题
POST http://localhost:8080/exam/answer
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2IiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJzdHVkZW50MSIsInJvbGUiOiJzdHVkZW50IiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzMzI0MDg2LCJleHAiOjE3ODM0MTA0ODZ9.i_Ok0y_P50oElRTVLM3JcIT1ngJYPUAeuLTZaA1suEY

{
  "examRecordId": 2074042573100019713,
  "questionId": 2074028802650501122,
  "userAnswer": "B"
}

###

### 3. 交卷（自动批改）
POST http://localhost:8080/exam/submit/2074042573100019713
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2IiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJzdHVkZW50MSIsInJvbGUiOiJzdHVkZW50IiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzMzI0MDg2LCJleHAiOjE3ODM0MTA0ODZ9.i_Ok0y_P50oElRTVLM3JcIT1ngJYPUAeuLTZaA1suEY

# 返回结果包含：
#   totalScore — 总分
#   correctCount — 正确题数
#   totalCount — 总题数
#   answers[] — 每道题的批改详情（用户答案/正确答案/是否得分）

###

### 4. 考试详情（查看批改结果）
GET http://localhost:8080/exam/record/2074042573100019713
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2IiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJzdHVkZW50MSIsInJvbGUiOiJzdHVkZW50IiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzMzI0MDg2LCJleHAiOjE3ODM0MTA0ODZ9.i_Ok0y_P50oElRTVLM3JcIT1ngJYPUAeuLTZaA1suEY

###

### 5. 我的考试记录
GET http://localhost:8080/exam/my-list
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2IiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJzdHVkZW50MSIsInJvbGUiOiJzdHVkZW50IiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzMzI0MDg2LCJleHAiOjE3ODM0MTA0ODZ9.i_Ok0y_P50oElRTVLM3JcIT1ngJYPUAeuLTZaA1suEY

###

### ============================================
### 异常场景测试
### ============================================

### 6. 重复开始同一试卷（应返回 resume=true 断点续考）
POST http://localhost:8080/exam/start
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2IiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJzdHVkZW50MSIsInJvbGUiOiJzdHVkZW50IiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzMzI0MDg2LCJleHAiOjE3ODM0MTA0ODZ9.i_Ok0y_P50oElRTVLM3JcIT1ngJYPUAeuLTZaA1suEY

{
  "paperId": 2074035342996443137
}

###

### 7. 对已提交的考试保存答案（应报错"考试已结束"）
POST http://localhost:8080/exam/answer
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2IiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJzdHVkZW50MSIsInJvbGUiOiJzdHVkZW50IiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzMzI0MDg2LCJleHAiOjE3ODM0MTA0ODZ9.i_Ok0y_P50oElRTVLM3JcIT1ngJYPUAeuLTZaA1suEY

{
  "examRecordId": 2074039714098835457,
  "questionId": 2074028794681323521,
  "userAnswer": "B"
}

###

### 8. 重复交卷（应报错"考试已提交过"）
POST http://localhost:8080/exam/submit/2074039714098835457
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2IiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJzdHVkZW50MSIsInJvbGUiOiJzdHVkZW50IiwiaWF0IjoxNzgzMzI0MDg2LCJleHAiOjE3ODM0MTA0ODZ9.i_Ok0y_P50oElRTVLM3JcIT1ngJYPUAeuLTZaA1suEY
